copy orgmgmt\* to project\

install db-schema\install_org.sql

Web Pages\jsff\menu.xhtml: 增加組織管理選單 (系統管理員, 使用者管理下方)
                <p:menuitem value="#{msgOrgmgmt['orgmgmt.title']}" url="/faces/org/management.xhtml"
                            rendered="#{userSession.isUserInRole('ADMINISTRATORS')}"/>

Configuration Files\faces-config.xml, 增加msgOrgmgmt
        <resource-bundle>
            <description>message for org management</description>
            <base-name>msgOrgmgmt</base-name>
            <var>msgOrgmgmt</var>
        </resource-bundle>

Configuration Files\persistence.xml, 增加下列 entity
        <class>com.tcci.fc.entity.org.OrgCompany</class>
        <class>com.tcci.fc.entity.org.OrgDepartment</class>
        <class>com.tcci.fc.entity.org.OrgEmployee</class>

Configuration Files\web.xml, /faces/org/* 權限控管 (可將ADMINISTRATORS合併在一起)
    <security-constraint>
        <web-resource-collection>
            <web-resource-name>使用者管理, 組織管理</web-resource-name>
            <url-pattern>/faces/usermgmt/*</url-pattern>
            <url-pattern>/faces/org/*</url-pattern>
        </web-resource-collection>
        <auth-constraint>
            <role-name>ADMINISTRATORS</role-name>
        </auth-constraint>
    </security-constraint>

Clean & Build, Run
系統管理員 > 組織管理
公司匯入: db-schema\companyImport.xlsx
部門匯入: db-schema\departmentImport.xlsx
員工匯入: db-schema\employeeImport.xlsx